text: Karsbach is a municipality in Main-Spessart in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Gemünden am Main. == Geography == === Location === Karsbach is in the Würzburg Region. The community has the following Ortsteile and Gemarkungen (traditional rural cadastral areas): Heßdorf, Höllrich, Karsbach, Weyersfeld. == References == Category:Main-Spessart
title: Karsbach
